  <p align="left">                                       INCEDO - MISSION GIVING OPTIONS</p>
  <p align="left"><strong>Background</strong><br>
    Youth for Christ&rsquo;s &ldquo;system&rdquo; of mission giving was that every base (centre) gave a monthly A/P into a centralised fund. Out of this, YFC was able to contribute around $23,000 per year to a variety of overseas YFC groups and missions. When we changed from YFC to Incedo, this A/P system stopped. A few bases have continued to send in A/Ps and our general fund has continued to support YFC in Fiji, Samoa, Nepal and Myanmar.</p>
  <p align="left"><strong>Proposal</strong><br>
    Our desire is to involve bases in a more personal connection of mission giving. The issue is not the amount, but that we all take the challenge of both giving something, and getting to know missionaries in other countries.</p>
  <p align="left"><strong>How does it work?</strong><br>
    Incedo people at your base select one or more recipients from the list below, and decide how much you will give per month. You can either action an A/P to Incedo and it will be used to support our existing commitments, or you can organize an A/P directly to one of the people below. Whichever you do, please let Incedo know (email<a href="mailto:t.bedford@incedo.org.nz"> t.bedford@incedo.org.nz</a>). Once every base has done that, Incedo leadership will decide what additional giving we will provide from General Funds.</p>
  <p align="left"><strong>Time Frame</strong><br>
    We would like you to action this no later than January 31 next year.</p>
